{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji41.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于调演豫剧《破洪州》给周恩来的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于调演豫剧《破洪州》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给周恩来的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1959年4月24日）总理："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在郑州看过一次戏，穆桂英挂帅，叫做《破洪州》，颇好，是一个改造过的戏，主角常香玉扮穆桂英。我看可以调这个班子来京为人大代表演一次。如你同意，请处理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《破洪州》剧本仍有缺点，待后可商量修改。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月二十四日[1]常香玉，豫剧表演艺术家，当时任河南豫剧院院长。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":24}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":462,"page_end":462},"tags":[{"name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}